        <mxCell id="callout_text" value="✅ Push connector (not pull)&#xa;     Full control, no preview dependency&#xa;&#xa;✅ No Blob intermediary&#xa;     SharePoint → memory → index&#xa;&#xa;✅ Zero secrets for Azure services&#xa;     Managed Identity + RBAC only&#xa;&#xa;✅ Flex Consumption (FC1)&#xa;     Scales to zero, pay per execution&#xa;&#xa;✅ Incremental sync + reconciliation&#xa;     Efficient hourly updates" style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;fontStyle=0;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#333333;spacingLeft=5;spacingTop=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
